= March 2019}}\n{{Infobox musical artist\n| name             = Akhil\n| image            = \n| caption          = \n| background       = solo_singer\n| alias            = Akhil Pasricha\n| birth_date       = \n| birth_place      = \n| origin           = \n| genre            = [[Pop music|Pop]], [[Hip hop music|Hip Hop]], [[Bhangra (music)|Bhangra]]\n| occupation       = {{flatlist|\n* Actor\n* Singer\n* Songwriter\n* Music composer\n}}\n| instrument       = \n| years_active     = 2013\u2014present\n| label            = [[T-Series (company)|T-Series]]<br>Tru Makers<br>Speed Records<br>Crown Records\n| associated_acts  = [[Ikka Singh|Ikka]]<br>[[Adah Sharma]] [[Manni Sandhu]]\n| website          = {{url|http://facebook.com/Akhil Official01}}<br>{{url|http://instagram.com/a.k.h.i.l_01}}\n}}\n\n'''Akhil Pasricha''', known mononymously as '''Akhil''',<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/khwaab-singer-akhils-gig-police-thrashing-unruly-crowd-bring-dramatic-end-to-kmc-fest/articleshow/68429109.cms|title=Khaab singer Akhil\u2019s gig, police thrashing unruly crowd bring dramatic end to KMC fest - Times of India \u25ba|website=The Times of India}}</ref> is an Indian actor, playback singer, songwriter and music performer.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/topic/Akhil|title=Akhil: Latest News, Videos and Photos of Akhil &#124; Times of India|website=The Times of India}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patrika.com/bikaner-news/punjabi-singer-akhils-songs-in-bikaner-2010235/|title=\u092c\u0940\u0915\u093e\u0928\u0947\u0930 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0902\u091c\u093e\u092c\u0940 \u0938\u093f\u0902\u0917\u0930 \u0905\u0916\u093f\u0932 \u0915\u0947 \u0917\u093e\u0928\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0940 \u092e\u091a\u0947\u0917\u0940 \u0927\u0942\u092e|website=www.patrika.com}}</ref> He made his [[Music of Bollywood|Bollywood singing]] debut in ''[[Luka Chuppi]]'' (2019).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.in.com/entertainment/regional/after-sunanda-punjabi-singers-karan-and-akhil-step-into-bollywood-328701.htm|title=After Sunanda, Punjabi singers Karan and Akhil step into Bollywood|website=in.com}}</ref>\n\n== Early life ==\n\nAkhil was born on 2 October in 1990 in [[Jalandhar]], [[Punjab]], [[India]]. He completed his school education from \u201cArya Senior Secondary School\" in Nurmahal, [[Jalandhar]]. Then he completed his graduation from APJ College of Fine Arts.{{Citation needed|date=March 2019}}\n\n== Career ==\n\nIn February 2014, his first single \"Muradaan \" was released under HSR Entertainment (formerly Yellow Music).<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.catchnews.com/bollywood-news/luka-chuppi-songs-singer-akhil-s-khaab-is-now-kartik-aaryan-and-kriti-sanon-s-duniyaa-150251.html|title=Luka Chuppi Songs: Singer Akhil's 'Khaab' is now Kartik Aaryan and Kriti Sanon's 'Duniyaa'|website=CatchNews.com}}</ref>He previously sang a song titled \"Pee Lain De\" in 2012 though.<ref>{{Citation|title=Akhil Pasricha {{!}} Pee Lain De {{!}} OFFICIAL VIDEO {{!}} 2012|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eyDgXjMylTQ|language=en|access-date=2020-01-22}}</ref> \n\nHis Punjabi-language single \"Khaab\", which was released in February 2016 became popular on [[YouTube]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timesnownews.com/entertainment/news/bollywood-news/article/check-out-kartik-aaryan-kriti-sanons-sizzling-chemistry-in-this-exclusive-still-from-luka-chuppi-song-duniya/370484|title=Luka Chuppi song Duniyaa: Kartik Aaryan and Kriti Sanon's sizzling chemistry will leave you impressed &#124; Bollywood News|website=www.timesnownews.com}}</ref> In February 2019, a Hindi remake of ''Khaab'', ''Duniyaa'', was recorded for the film ''[[Luka Chuppi]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ptcpunjabi.co.in/akhil-steps-into-bollywood-with-khaab-remake-for-luka-chuppi/|title=Akhil Steps Into Bollywood With Khaab Remake For Luka Chuppi|first=Diksha|last=Kapoor|date=22 February 2019}}</ref>\n\nIn June 2016, he collaborated with music composer \"[[Manni Sandhu]]\" for a single titled \"Gani\" for his album ''Welcome To The Future'', released by Speed Records.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.in.com/entertainment/regional/akhil-screws-up-his-khaab-by-letting-bollywood-recreate-it-as-duniya-323077.htm|title=Akhil screws up his 'Khaab' by letting Bollywood recreate it as 'Duniya'!|website=in.com}}</ref> A year later, he released the single \"Life\" starring bollywood actress [[Adah Sharma]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://chandigarhmetro.com/life-punjabi-song-by-akhil-heres-the-official-video/|title=Life (Punjabi Song) by Akhil - Here's the Official Video of the New Song|date=16 June 2017|website=Chandigarh Metro}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://chandigarhmetro.com/life-punjabi-song-by-akhil-heres-the-official-video/|title=Life (Punjabi Song) by Akhil - Here's the Official Video of the New Song|date=16 June 2017}}</ref>\n\n== Discography ==\n\n===Film Songs===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Film\n!Track\n!Co-Singer(s)\n!Label\n!Notes\n|-\n|2016\n|[[Vaapsi]]\n|''Saari Saari Raat'' \n|\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Speed Records\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Punjabi Movies\n|-\n|2017\n|[[Jindua]]\n|''Takdi Ravan''\n|[[Jonita Gandhi]]\n|-\n|2018\n|[[Ishqaa]]\n|''Ishqaa''\n|\n|[[Times Music]]\n|-\n|2019\n|Luka Chuppi\n|''Duniyaa''\n|[[Dhvani Bhanushali]]\n|[[T-Series (company)|T-Series]]\n|Bollywood Debut\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Singles ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#cfc; text-align:center;\"\n!Year\n!Track\n!Featuring\n!Label\n!Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2014\n|''Muradaan''\n|\n|HSR Entertainment (formerly Yellow Music)\n|\n|-\n|''Supne''\n|\n|HSR Entertainment (formerly Yellow Music)\n|\n|-\n|2016\n|''Khaab''\n|\n|Crown Records\n|''<small>Breakthrough single</small>''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2016\n|''Makhaul''\n|\n| rowspan=\"11\" |Speed Records\n|\n|-\n|''Gani''\n|\n|-\n|''Teri Kami''\n|\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |2017\n|''Zindagi''\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.radioandmusic.com/entertainment/editorial/news/180214-pu